name: TelNet Worldwide
overview: TelNet Worldwide, Inc. provides comprehensive communications products and services for businesses. The company offers traditional telephony services and innovative IP-based solutions, such as voice and data, T1 Internet, hosted PBX, PRI connections, private line, local service, collocation, conferencing, digital fax to email, and enhanced services, as well as professional services, including technical consultation, network design, installation, and support services. Its voice and data services include business communications solutions, which include local, long distance, and high-speed Internet access. The company serves manufacturers, healthcare facilities, marketing services, law firms, Internet-based companies, companies that require various phone lines, corporate offices, multi-location businesses, hospitals, schools, design firms, financial institutions, service industry, companies with business travelers, companies w/off-site employees, apartment management, and commercial property owner/management companies. TelNet owns and operates Superior Contact, offering comprehensive contact management and call center services, 24/7. TelNet Worldwide has strategic partnerships with GENBAND, BROADSOFT, TouchStar, ADTRAN and BillSoft Incorporated, to name a few. The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Troy, Michigan.

acquisitions.source_description: TelNet Worldwide Acquires DigitalRealm Accelerating Product Development and Growth
